# CLAUDE.md Example

This is an example CLAUDE.md file that the prompt optimizer will read.

## Project Patterns

### State Management
- Use Zustand for global state (not Redux)
- Component-local state for UI-only concerns
- Never store map instances in useState (use useRef)

### Common Mistakes
- ❌ Using `amenity=supermarket` (wrong OSM tag)
- ✅ Using `shop=supermarket` (correct OSM tag)

### Architecture
- Map.tsx: Single Mapbox GL JS instance (ref-based)
- ConfigPanel.tsx: Connects to Zustand store
- osmService.ts: OpenStreetMap API client (rate limited)

## Development Workflow

When fixing bugs:
1. Always check console for errors first
2. Verify file paths match actual structure
3. Run `npm run build` to catch TypeScript errors

When adding features:
1. Update TypeScript interfaces first
2. Add to Zustand store if global state needed
3. Consider dark mode support (project uses Tailwind v4)

## Testing
- Run `npm run lint` before committing
- Manual testing required (no automated tests yet)

This context helps the prompt optimizer understand project-specific patterns
and guide users accordingly.
